A	O
voice	O
activity	O
detector	O
(	O
VAD	O
)	O
which	O
determines	O
whether	O
received	O
voice	O
signal	O
samples	O
contain	O
speech	O
by	O
deriving	O
parameters	O
measuring	O
short	O
term	O
time	O
domain	O
characteristics	O
of	O
the	O
input	O
signal	O
,	O
including	O
the	O
average	O
signal	O
level	O
and	O
the	O
absolute	O
value	O
of	O
any	O
change	O
in	O
average	O
signal	O
level	O
,	O
and	O
comparing	O
the	O
derived	O
parameter	O
values	O
with	O
corresponding	O
thresholds	O
,	O
which	O
are	O
periodically	O
monitored	O
and	O
updated	O
to	O
reflect	O
changes	O
in	O
the	O
level	O
of	O
background	O
noise	O
,	O
thereby	O
minimizing	O
clipping	O
and	O
false	O
alarms	O
.	O

